text: Lise-Lotte Djerf (born 17 March 1963) is a Swedish archer. Djerf competed at the 1992 Summer Olympics.Lise-Lotte DjerfLise-Lotte ANDERSSON-DJERF ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1963 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish archers Category:Olympians for Sweden
